g.text: An Idle / Cooking Game about making noodles
Mobile Responsive Phaser Game
Game starts with showing a circle's lower half
protruding from the top of the screen, representing
some dough
The player can pull down on the screen or
click and drag with the mouse to bring the
dough to the center. The dough can only move down
and not move to the sides.
Once the dough is in the center, it locks there.
The player can then drag on the dough to rotate it.
Rotating the dough makes it bigger and bigger
and increases the progress bar.
Once the progress bar is complete, the dough
can't be rotated anymore. The player can then
drag the item to the right to the end of the screen.
Dragging it all the way increases the rolled doughs
by 1, and allows the player to drag more dough from
the top of the screen.
